| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4350 — Recovery Inhibition (bianlian)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: f9e9ebdc-fad4-5962-a3cd-6b39f866e2eb"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
